text: Vladislav Kulikov (born 8 July 1996) is a Russian professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI ProTeam . He rode in the men's team pursuit event at the 2017 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. ==Major results== ===Road=== ;2018 : 2nd Under-23 National Time Trial Championships : 6th Overall Five Rings of Moscow ===Track=== ;2017 : World Cup ::3rd Team pursuit, Cali : National Championships ::2nd Scratch ::3rd Individual pursuit ::3rd Team pursuit ::3rd Madison ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
